{"tid":355520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點撚解啲人咁撚鍾意sd　錄音俾人","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T11:33:53.000Z","uid":133611,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce71a1773f883f8c7e0daafa02ae19f3436de11b","tid":355520,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"尤其是啲客<br />\n如果係fd　對　fd都還好<br />\n你一句我一句<br />\n客真係寧舍鍾意錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1）屌你老味俾嘢人做通常都唔會得一句嘢要講㗎啦<br />\n逐句錄都算啦　你之後醒起有嘢要加番落point 1 point 2 度<br />\n又要之後加多個錄音 　　d 次序亂哂<br />\n<br />\n2）仲要聽你d　「er.......」<br />\n「點講好呢？」「好似.....」<br />\n「呀我醒起喇」　<br />\n咁多廢話　浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n3）唔係個個地方都適合你錄音㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲又細聲側邊又嘈<br />\n大佬要重覆聽你講N　次<br />\n<br />\n4）我跟你order　做嘢　有時要check番啲細項又要聽番你啲錄音<br />\n大佬　你百鳩幾個錄音<br />\n點知邊個打邊個？？又要人逐個聽番去confirm　你講咩嚟　<br />\n聽N　個錄音搵一個details　<br />\n是否戇鳩？<br />\n<br />\n頭先有條友（又係客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）同我講話覺得錄音好過打字<br />\n睇下佢咩戇鳩point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1）有語言之後先有文字　文字係代替品嚟咋<br />\n2）講嘢都唔夠清楚咩？咁你平時講嘢唔得啦，咩都要寫字啦<br />\n3）要人打字咁麻煩，講嘢夠方便，㩒個制就錄到<br />\n4）我用手寫　打字好慢　（屌，學打字啦仆街）<br />\n5）我無咁多時間同你打字　（屌你　你嘅就係時間，人地嘅就唔係？）<br />\n<br />\n完全係方便自己　麻鳩煩人地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自私精先會講呢啲垃圾point</span></span></strong>　 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8401922cb04e7508706b41f88ae1f12ea95ce4","tid":355520,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea